                {
                  "text": "Conduct full SEO optimization for medical queries",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Launch Google Ads campaigns to attract requests in different cities of Ukraine",
